## Validation Checklist

Before ending session, verify:
- ✅ Did I discuss before implementing code changes?
- ✅ Did I wait for approval before implementing?
- ✅ Did I consolidate into existing docs instead of creating new files?
- ✅ Are all new files referenced in PROJECT_SUMMARY.md or FEATURE_OVERVIEW.md?
- ✅ Did I avoid creating session summaries or temporary docs?
- ✅ Did I only update docs for major milestones (not every small change)?
- ✅ If PROJECT_SUMMARY.md changed significantly, did I update PROJECTS_OVERVIEW.md?

